reviews.text: Went for a Hainanese chicken rice, chicken was nice but they provide plain rice instead of chicken oil rice.
Singapore and Thai food is available, taste not bad, price not cheap
Nice environment, prawn cakes nice too, but was disappointed by the Laksa.
The Hainanese chicken rice is great! The chicken and rice are ordered separately.
Pad thai is quite ok

reviews.text: 海南雞飯好味👍👍
午餐海南雞飯套餐👌

Very standard South East Asian food (mainly Malaysian/Singaporean with a bit of Thai dessert thrown in), nothing to be surprised about. 
2 hours later I found myself completely cotton-mouthed. It's like a spider had weaved a web inside of my mouth. There has to be something wrong with the ingredient. 
非常普通，無什驚奇，吃完口裡感覺非常乾，肯定用了很多味精。 不會再去。
中午叫咗香茅豬扒飯好似豬肉乾咁，有一半係咬唔落， 香茅豬扒飯可以完全唔落豉油，勁差，仲要收58，無野飲，食個麥當勞冇咁嬲。

餐廳水杯污糟
椒鹽鮑魚同椒鹽軟殼蟹唔抵食
